                    "active": true,
                    "position": -60
                },
                {
                    "type": "actorAction",
                    "target": 2,
                    "expression": 0,
                    "active": true,
                    "position": 50
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": 0,
            "statement": "It was Esposito.",
            "action": [
                {
                    "type": "propAction",
                    "target": 0
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": 0,
            "statement": "As we know, Esposito was running a large scale drug operation, and Gerard Little was one of potentially several corrupt technicians within the Future*Tech system.",
            "action": [
                {
                    "type": "propAction",
                    "target": 1
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": 1,
            "statement": "However, Gerard Little started getting a little too confident in his abilities and started skimming off the top of Esposito's profits.",
            "action": [
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": 1,
            "statement": "Esposito found out, and naturally he was not pleased.",
            "action": [
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": 0,
            "statement": "He arranged to meet Gerard at one of his properties on the outskirts of town and proceeded to enact his revenge.",
            "action": [
                {
                    "type": "propAction",
                    "target": 2
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": 0,
            "statement": "Using a wrench at the scene, he beat Gerard Little to within an inch of his life.",
            "action": [
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": 1,
            "statement": "It was Esposito's turn to be a little too confident however.",
            "action": [
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": 1,
            "statement": "Rather than finishing the job, he decided to let his victim bleed out slowly for maximum pain and punishment.",
            "action": [
                {
                    "type": "propAction",
                    "target": -1
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": 0,
            "statement": "What he didn't count on however was that after he left, Gerard Little would use the last of his strength to drag himself to his Future*Tech car and order it to return to his workstation.",
            "action": [
                {
                    "type": "propAction",
                    "target": 5
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": 0,
            "statement": "Even though he wasn't able to save himself, we were able to follow leads found by examining the car that led to this conclusion.",
            "action": [
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": 2,
            "statement": "Good work team. Using your findings, we should be able to build a solid case against Esposito and put him away for good.",
            "action": [
                {
                    "type": "propAction",
                    "target": -1
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": 2,
            "statement": "Wait a second. I'm getting a notification.",
            "action": [
                {
                    "type": "actorAction",
                    "target": 2,
                    "expression": 4,
                    "active": true,
                    "position": 50
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": 2,
            "statement": "What?! No!",
            "action": [
                {
                    "type": "actorAction",
                    "target": 0,
                    "expression": 4,
                    "active": true,
                    "position": -20
                },
                {
                    "type": "actorAction",
